        "text_4pYVYF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Founded in 2000, Grasscity helped pioneer the online headshop industry, giving enthusiasts a new way to discover and order smoking accessories discreetly online. Today, Grasscity offers one of the largest selections of smoking gear, including bongs, vaporizers, dab rigs, glass pipes, and smoking accessories from trusted brands around the world.</p><p>Our catalog features respected European glass brands such as ROOR, EHLE, Black Leaf, and Blaze Glass, alongside well-known American makers including GRAV, Medicali, Jerome Baker Designs, and Cheech & Chong. From compact mini bongs and classic beaker bongs to advanced percolator bongs and durable silicone pieces, Grasscity brings together quality craftsmanship, functional design, and reliable value in one destination.</p><p>Whether you're upgrading your setup or discovering your first piece, Grasscity remains a trusted place to explore smoking accessories chosen with experience and care.</p>",
            "subtext_color": true
          }
        },
